``` src/main/java/com/teamname/furniviz/ ├── storage/ │ ├── RoomRepository.java ✅ (existing - reference) │ ├── DesignModel.java ⭐ CREATE (new) │ ├── DesignStorage.java ⭐ CREATE (new) │ ├── DesignModel.java ✅ (existing) │ └── JsonUtil.java ✅ (existing) │ ├── portfolio/ │ └── PortfolioPanel.java ⭐ IMPLEMENT (update) │ ├── app/ │ ├── Navigator.java ⚠️ EDIT (add portfolio route) │ ├── DesignState.java ✅ (use for state) │ └── MainFrame.java ✅ (existing) │ ├── editor2d/ │ └── Editor2DPanel.java ⚠️ EDIT (add save button) │ └── demo/ └── DemoPortfolio.java ⭐ CREATE (for testing) ```
