## Testing Strategy
### Unit Tests (Without UI)
```java // DemoPortfolio.java DesignStorage storage = new DesignStorage();
// Test 1: Save design Design d1 = new Design(...); assert storage.saveDesign(d1) == true;
// Test 2: Retrieve design Design retrieved = storage.getDesignById(d1.getDesignId()); assert retrieved != null;
// Test 3: Get user designs (multi-user) List<Design> userDesigns = storage.getDesignsByUserId("user-1"); assert userDesigns.size() == 1;
// Test 4: Search List<Design> found = storage.searchByName("user-1", "Living"); assert found.size() > 0;
// Test 5: Update d1.setDesignName("Updated"); storage.updateDesign(d1); assert storage.getDesignById(d1.getDesignId()).getDesignName() .equals("Updated");
// Test 6: Delete storage.deleteDesign(d1.getDesignId()); assert storage.getDesignById(d1.getDesignId()) == null; ```
### Integration Tests (With UI)
``` 1. Create room → Save design → View in portfolio ✓ Design appears in grid ✓ Thumbnail shows ✓ Count updates
2. Search designs ✓ Filter works correctly ✓ Grid updates
3. Sort designs ✓ "Date (Newest)" shows latest first ✓ "Name (A-Z)" shows alphabetically
4. Edit design ✓ Click edit → loads in editor ✓ Modify furniture ✓ Save again → updates design
5. Delete design ✓ Confirmation dialog appears ✓ Design removed from grid ✓ Count updates ```
---
## Performance Considerations
### For Future Optimization
1. **Lazy Loading Images** ```java // Don't load all thumbnails at once // Load thumbnails on demand when card becomes visible // Use SwingWorker for async image loading ```
2. **Pagination** ```java // For users with 100+ designs // Show 12-15 per page // Add Previous/Next buttons ```
3. **Caching** ```java // Cache DesignStorage in memory (HashMap) // Don't reload from DB every time // Invalidate cache when design changes ```
4. **Database Integration** ```java // Replace HashMap with MongoDB // Use indexes on userId, designName // Query optimization ```
---
## Error Handling Checklist
- [ ] Null checks for user ID - [ ] Null checks for design objects - [ ] File I/O errors (when exporting) - [ ] Image processing errors (thumbnails) - [ ] Storage failures (show user-friendly error) - [ ] Empty design name validation - [ ] Duplicate design name handling - [ ] Delete confirmation (prevent accidents)
---
## UI/UX Improvements (Optional)
1. **Drag & Drop**: Reorder designs 2. **Batch Operations**: Delete multiple at once 3. **Tagging**: Organize by categories 4. **Sharing**: Share designs with others 5. **Versioning**: Keep history of changes 6. **Comments**: Add notes to designs 7. **Favorites**: Star important designs 8. **Export Formats**: JSON, Image, PDF
